'''Uzee Usman Adeyemi''' (azán wídopotọ, Abọ̀húsun, 1986) yin aihundatọ [[Naijilia|Naijilianu]] dé, podọ anadenanutọ tito aihundida tọn dé he yè yọnẹn na aihun etọn dé he hosọ etọn yin '' Oga Abuja''. Nugopipe etọn nado doyẹyigona ''Nollywood'' po ''Kannywood'' po zọn bọ e mọ ajọ̀ susu yi podọ e yin yẹyidogona taidi ''Young Entrepreneur of the Year'' to hunwhẹ ''National Heritage Award'' tọn to 2016.







